Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.95,0:00:07.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:09.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma! Nikdy som si nemyslel, že...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:24.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hádam si si nemyslel, že budem veriť narodenému hnusnému bezkrídlemu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:30.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preklínam ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:37.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dosť dobré...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:44.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Gattai stvorenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:46.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideš! Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:52.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo! Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:57.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To svetlo stvorenia lieči moje rany?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:02.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vrátil sa späť do života!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.78,0:01:08.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:10.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:12.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo... Reika...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:16.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Báli ste sa o mňa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:17.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,O čom to hovoríš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:19.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravda! Sme priatelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:21.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpustite mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:25.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vitaj späť, Slnečné Krídlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preklínam ťa, Toma! Ideme!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:31.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre!\NDobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:38.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je rýchly!\NReika!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:47.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je silný!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslí to vážne!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:51.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:53.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tá vôňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:55.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chibiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:58.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš tvojho priateľa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:03.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo! Postaraj sa o Chibi a ostatných!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:06.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chibiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:08.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal "Chibiko"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:09.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:12.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chibiko! Maji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:16.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Už sa vzdávaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:17.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:19.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráť mi Chibiko a ostatných!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:23.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo... použi silu môjho meča!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Robíš to zaujímavým...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:45.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Detská hra!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:11.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Krásne...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:16.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto je určite svetlo môjho milovaného Slnečného Krídla!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:20.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Svetlo nádeje, ktoré nám vrátilo silu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:25.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Slnečné Krídlo sa prebudilo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:28.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeho peľ, s vlasnosťami, ktoré nám chýbajú
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:32.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,oplodnil strom života...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:37.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Noví Anjely, nový svet sa zrodí...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:40.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,My musíme ísť tiež k stromu životu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:48.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, aby sme boli pohltení koreňami, aby boli nové semiačka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:51.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,K stromu života!\NK stromu života!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:56.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,K stromu života!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa to preboha deje?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozrite! Strom života je...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:20.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:48.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak krásny...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:51.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dlho stratené, sväté ovocie bude...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:58.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:05:02.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Slnečné Krídlo získal svoje pravé svetlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:10.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeho opelenie prichádza s jeho pravým svetlom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:13.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nezomieraj, strom života!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:20.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:31.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Skončili ste!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:59.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabi ma, ak si tak praješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj tak svet dozná konca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým myslíš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:09.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Korene stromu života dosiahnu až na samú dreň síl tejto planéty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:14.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak strom zomrie, tak táto sila prejde do zeme
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:18.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a premení povrch na zem bez života.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!\NTo je absurdné!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:22.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Strom života je...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:37.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Abnormálna aktivita v zemskom plášti!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Úroveň skreslenia stúpa vo všetkých vrstvách!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pri tomto tempe budú katastrofálne pohyby zemskej kôry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:48.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Museli poraziť strom života...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:51.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Svet končí...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:59.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Svet skončí.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si to povedal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň! Tým, že ho zabiješ, nič nezmeníš!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:06.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale povedal, že svet končí!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:08.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Stále...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre sa pozri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:18.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tá vôňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:19.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ťieňoví Anjely...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rovnaká vôňa ako z Tomy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:25.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bez Ťieňového Anjela na palube...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:31.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bez sily Ťieňového Anjela, Aquarion nie je kompletný!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:36.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokonca aj s odtrhnutými krídlami je to Ťieňový Anjel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.07,0:07:42.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zo všetkých vecí...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:49.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Naše Anjelské krídla boli potrebné, aby sa Slnečné Krídlo skutočne prebudilo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:08.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Luna ukazuje zmenu reakcie teleportu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto sa snaží teleportovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:12.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to... Ťieňový Anjel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo, ty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:23.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:33.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj tak nebudem žiť o moc dlhšie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:36.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikam nejdeš!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď si po mňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď so mnou do Gattai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:44.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Stanem sa Slnečným Krídlom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:50.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môj život môže byť pohltený stromom života...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem vidieť pravé prebudenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:55.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si v poriadku, Reika?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:58.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno. A ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráť sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem tiež!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:04.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:08.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:09.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:11.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechoď, Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:12.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:15.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Svet môže skončiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:17.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak pôjdem s tebou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím! Nenechávaj ma tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:25.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem. Chcem, aby si ochránila Chibiko a ostatných!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:31.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sľubil som to Baronovi, že ich zachránim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:38.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:42.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cíť 12.000 rokov zášti!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:50.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Následuj ma, bezkrídli...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme! Gattai stvorenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:59.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedostaneš šancu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:02.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebudeš hlava!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:12.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráť mi Barona, Chibiko a ostatných!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:14.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Drzý bezkrídly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:17.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pocíť, aké je to byť zradený!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetky 3 stroje Vector sa premenili na hlavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:28.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Turbulenica 3. citovej aury narastá!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:30.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Týmto tempom sa samy zničia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Narušenie vrcholí!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:37.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa to bude zhoršovať týmto tempom, svet bude... svet bude...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:49.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zober si to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:54.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si v poriadku, Silvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:58.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre... Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:04.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia... tieto krídla ti sedia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:15.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach, nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je... bezpilotný Vector!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:26.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:28.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten Cherubín...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...je späť!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prekliaty Ťieňový Anjel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:40.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Už nemôžem sedieť a pozerať...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:44.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rena?!\NRena?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prišla si pomôcť?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:51.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebolo ľahké sa teleportovať na takú vzdialenosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poďme sa o to rýchlo postarať.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vďaka, Rena. Tak to spravíme!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:56.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nenshin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:57.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Gattai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideš! Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cítim oheň!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cítim brnenie po celom tele!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Alfa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Znova ona?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je nič!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem, všetkým...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:32.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo... Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oheň!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:41.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabijem ich alebo pri tom zomriem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:44.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zmena! Chodec!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:04.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je hrozné... všetci sa rozdelili!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre sa pozeraj.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:09.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:17.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre sa pozeraj na bolesť spôsobenú Apolloniusom a Seliane pred 12.000 rokmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nenávisť!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:30.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A hĺbka temnoty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:47.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V ten čas, v ten deň, keď som 1. krát stretla Apolloniusa,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:53.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,cítila som z hĺbky srdca, že aj keď ma roztrhne na kusy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:57.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...aj keď svet príde do záhuby...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:03.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola som...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:10.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...šťastná, že som ho stretla!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:21.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď tlieskaš rukami, čo existuje medzi tým?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:23.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:27.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoja pravá a ľavá ruka, Anjely a ľudia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:31.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Muž a žena. Yin a Yang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je medzi nimi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:47.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cíť silu našich anjelských krídel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika, Pierre...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:53.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Použijem svoju silu, aby sme lietali v jej bariére.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:54.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Lietali?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:56.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Postarajte sa o zvyšok!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teleportovali sa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:05.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz je čas oddeliť sa od...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:06.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(321,160)}"Nešťastie"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:07.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...nešťastia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(321,179)}"Nešťastná B-Reika"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:23.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Niečo, čo existuje medzi mojou pravou a ľavou rukou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:33.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Medzi mojou pravou a ľavou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Temnota?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:48.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Medzi rukami, nie je... nič...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:52.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nič, ešte...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je tam teplo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Svetlo zrodené z tmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:26.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:36.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje drahocenné druhé ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:47.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hnusný bezkrídly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:49.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:52.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy ti nemôžem odpustiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem ti odpustiť, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:05.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Také teplé...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:17.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo, spomínaš si...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:20.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...na deň, kedy svet začal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:25.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Miliardy a miliardy hviezd, miliardy a miliardy galaxií...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:29.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...vytvorený v svätom momente z ničoty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten zázračný moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:33.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zázračný?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:38.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno. A zázrak toho...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:43.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,ako sme sa ty a ja stretli na tejto planéte!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:50.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A teraz... ideme vpred, po novej ceste!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:07.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A... to som si myslel, že pôjdem sám...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolesť a nenávisť, cítil som...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:18.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to bolesť spôsobená Tomom pred 12.000 rokmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:21.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy som nerozumel bezkrídlym...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:25.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ich bolesť, ich radosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:30.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy som nerozumel... bolesti anjelov, ktorá pretrvala, pretože vymreli...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:33.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Smútok matky zeme...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:39.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dostaň sa cez to! Gattai stvorenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Gattai stvorenia! Gattai stvorenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:44.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Gattai stvorenia?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:46.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci traja?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:52.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Beštie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...sa stali jendou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Gattai stvorenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:58.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideš!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:02.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy som necítil, že by sa mi takto rozbúšilo srdce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nová esencia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:22.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,My sme...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:25.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...živí!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:34.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Gattai Solar Aquariona hotový!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:36.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sila áur stúpa. Prekročila grafy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:41.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neuveriteľné... Anjely a ľudia ako jeden...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:50.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neuveriteľné!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Slnečné Krídlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:05.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:07.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem, Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:08.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:18.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Túto známu vôňu... Už nikdy nezabudnem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:18.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apol-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:44.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak všetko pôjde dobre, stretneme sa znova o 12.000 rokov!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:52.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme, priatelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:53.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre dobro ľudí a anjelov...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:54.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,tejto planéty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:57.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nové stvorenie!\NNové stvorenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:00.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sme vesmírom"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:01.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(317,174)}"Nekonečný úder Gattai"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:18.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chibiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:20.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vďaka bohu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:22.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chibiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:25.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:27.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako vieš, kto som?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:32.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo mi ho povedal vo sne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:36.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V tvojom sne?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:41.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je Apollo? Kam zmizol?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:45.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:49.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,určite vráti...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:53.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedného dňa, na túto planétu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:42.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Deň, keď svet začal" "Dúfam, že bude pokračovať"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.87,0:23:51.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V 1. dni na svete, pod stromom života,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:57.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}dvaja z nás počuli hlasy veľrýb, odrážajúce sa z diaľky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:24:04.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}So všetkým, čo sme stratili a všetko, čo sme milovali,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:10.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}čo sme mali v náručí, kam sa to zatúľalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:17.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Odpoveď leží v jantári slnka.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:23.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Ak by som ťa nestretla, zničila by som anjela.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.50,0:24:29.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Moja duša posadnutá okamihom nesmrteľnosti,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:32.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}nezraní moje krídla.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.78,0:24:39.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Zrodila som sa, aby som spoznala tento pocit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.45,0:24:45.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po 1.000 rokov a ešte ďalších 2.000, som ťa ľúbila.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.79,0:24:52.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po 8.000 rokoch, som ťa ľúbila ešte viac.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.13,0:24:58.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po ďalších 100.000.000 rokov a ešte ďalších 2.000, ťa budem stále ľúbiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.47,0:25:07.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Od 1. dňa, keď som ťa spoznala, hudba v mojom pekle nikdy neprestala.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.01,0:25:09.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,
